2000.description: Eliminate all enemies along the naval route.
2000.name: Chapter 1-2 Deja Vu
2000.rare_task_text: Head towards the Bermuda waters while eliminating all enemies along the way.

2001.description: Gain control of the Bermuda Zone.
2001.name: Chapter 1-3 Back to Bermuda
2001.rare_task_text: Gain control of the Bermuda Zone and investigate the anomalies in the zone.

2002.description: Open the route to the central zone.
2002.name: Chapter 1-4 Crimson Shadow
2002.rare_task_text: Investigate the anomalous situation in the Bermudas and proceed as planned to open up a route to the central zone.

2003.description: Follow the Iron Blood Main Fleet.
2003.name: Chapter 1-5 Ceasefire Agreement
2003.rare_task_text: Recon planes discovered the Iron Blood’s Main Fleet hidden at sea. Prepare for battle - the other party’s intentions are unknown.

2004.description: Eliminate all enemies in this zone.
2004.name: Chapter 1-6 Outpost
2004.rare_task_text: The fleet has reached the waters just outside the central area of the NA Ocean. Eliminate all enemies to ensure the smooth establishment of an outpost in these waters.

2010.description: Successfully secure a number of zones within the NA Ocean SW Sector.
2010.name: Chapter 1-SP Establish Control!
2010.rare_task_text: Secure <color=#92fc63>8</color> zones in the NA Ocean SW Sector (Unlocks Chapter 2-1).

2050.description: Head to the NY City Port rally point.
2050.name: Chapter 1-1 Set Sail
2050.rare_task_text: Operation Siren is about to commence. Please lead your fleet to NY City Port to participate in the operation briefings.

2100.description: Assemble your fleet and prepare for battle.
2100.name: Chapter 2-1 Assemble!
2100.rare_task_text: All the preparations for battle have been completed. The Royal Navy will set off from Liverpool Port to join the fight!

2101.description: Rendezvous with the Iris Libre fleet.
2101.name: Chapter 2-2 Shoulder-to-Shoulder
2101.rare_task_text: The fleet from Iris Libre is about to arrive. Head to the rally point to join the allied fleet, and carry out the next step of the operation.

2102.description: Clear the enemies in the surrounding waters.
2102.name: Chapter 2-3 Peripheral Sweep
2102.rare_task_text: The fleets fought well, successfully clearing enemies from the surrounding waters before advancing towards the central zone.

2103.description: Search for the source of the SOS Signal.
2103.name: Chapter 2-4 SOS Signal
2103.rare_task_text: After receiving a distress signal, you grouped up with the Iris Libre fleet to carry out a joint rescue mission.

2104.description: Eliminate all enemies in this zone.
2104.name: Chapter 2-5 Queen’s Contact
2104.rare_task_text: We’ve detected a large number of Siren fleets garrisoned outside of the central zone. Clear them out to ensure that the operation continues smoothly.

2105.description: Secure the deployment of the Outpost.
2105.name: Chapter 2-6 Formidable Foe
2105.rare_task_text: An unknown anomaly has hindered the deployment of the second outpost. Head to the next zone to investigate the cause, and make sure the plan goes smoothly.

2110.description: Successfully secure a number of zones within the NA Ocean NE Sector.
2110.name: Chapter 2-SP Establish Control!
2110.rare_task_text: Secure <color=#92fc63>8</color> zones in the NA Ocean NE Sector (Unlocks Chapter 3-1).

2150.log_text: Issue a Fleet Redeployment order by the port and change your fleet composition.
2150.name: Fleet Size Expansion
2150.rare_task_text: Use Fleet Deployment while at Port to unlock the 4th Fleet.

2200.description: Prepare your fleet and get ready for battle.
2200.name: Chapter 3-1 Another Assault
2200.rare_task_text: The battle has begun, and your fleet has set sail. The fleets headed towards Sector C are making their final combat preparations.

2201.description: Learn the functionalities of Navigator TB, and break through the Siren defenses.
2201.name: Chapter 3-2 Navigator TB
2201.rare_task_text: The Siren’s defensive line was no match for you, and this proved to be a good opportunity to familiarize yourself with Navigator TB’s functionalities while sweeping the area of enemies.

2202.description: Investigate the friendly signals received from this zone.
2202.name: Chapter 3-3 Friendly Signal
2202.rare_task_text: Navigator TB detected a friendly signal moving in a nearby zone. Pay attention to its movement while continuing to fight off enemy forces.

2203.name: Chapter 3-4 Rescue
2203.rare_task_text: Ark Royal was encircled by Sirens while alone. Immediately muster a fleet to perform a rescue mission.

2204.description: Locate and eliminate the source of the jamming.
2204.name: Chapter 3-5 Afterimage
2204.rare_task_text: The situation is critical - locate and eliminate the source of the jamming with due haste.

2205.description: Eliminate all enemies in this zone.
2205.name: Chapter 3-6 One Fell Swoop
2205.rare_task_text: The Siren command structure has finally come back online, but it is already too late. Eliminate the rest of the enemies and secure the establishment of the Outpost.

2210.description: Successfully secure a number of zones within the NA Ocean NW Sector.
2210.name: Chapter 3-SP Establish Control!
2210.rare_task_text: Secure <color=#92fc63>8</color> zones in the NA Ocean NW Sector (Unlocks Chapter 4-1).

2300.description: Head to the port of the Sardegna Empire.
2300.name: Chapter 4-1 Glimpses of Méditerranée
2300.rare_task_text: Don’t harbor any unrealistic expectations for outsiders. Only you can fight for your own interests. Take the first steps to uncover the mysteries in the waters of the NA Ocean by heading to Sardegna to sign a ceasefire agreement.

2301.name: Chapter 4-2 Taranto Harbor
2301.rare_task_text: Both the Royal Navy and the Iron Blood fleets are en route to Taranto. Get the ceasefire agreement out of the way - only then can the truly important work begin.

2302.name: Chapter 4-3 Dakar Port
2302.rare_task_text: After “escaping” from the endless Sardegnian banquet, you sailed to Port Dakar in the Vichya Dominion to receive the “gift” from the Iron Blood.

2303.description: Carry out an independent combat operation.
2303.name: Chapter 4-4 Penetration
2303.rare_task_text: The Iron Blood fleet showed no interest of joining forces. With that being the case, the Sakura Empire undertook its own combat operations after resupplying.

2304.name: Chapter 4-5 Sea Fog
2304.rare_task_text: Don’t worry about stragglers - stay in formation, and continue towards the center of the zone!

2305.name: Chapter 4-6 Strategic Shift
2305.rare_task_text: The heavy sea fog in this region not only has hallucinogenic effects and disrupting the fleet formation, but also strongly interfering with our electronic equipment. We’ll have to find everyone before we can decide what to do next.

2310.description: Successfully secure a number of zones within the NA Ocean SE Sector.
2310.name: Chapter 4-SP Establish Control!
2310.rare_task_text: Secure <color=#92fc63>8</color> zones in the NA Ocean SE Sector (Subsequent chapters will be unlocked at a future date).

2600.description: Await instructions at the Eagle Union's forward base
2600.name: Chapter 5-1 - Bogged Down
2600.rare_task_text: Remain on standby at the Eagle Union's forward base while waiting for orders.

2601.name: Chapter 5-2 - Coordinates
2601.rare_task_text: Perform reconnaissance of the Siren-occupied zone to figure out the size of their force.

2602.name: Chapter 5-3 - The Phantom
2602.rare_task_text: Find out what the Ashes member, Hiryuu, is here for.

2603.description: Wait at the Royal Navy's forward base
2603.name: Chapter 5-4 - Teatime
2603.rare_task_text: Wait for your allies to finish preparing for the all-out offensive at the Royal Navy's forward base.

2604.name: Chapter 5-5 - All-Out Offensive
2604.rare_task_text: Launch an all-out attack on the Siren-occupied zone.

2605.description: Investigate the NA Ocean Core Sector
2605.name: Chapter 5-6-0 - Torus
2605.rare_task_text: Secure the Siren-occupied zone and investigate the sector.

2606.name: Chapter 5-6-1 - Point of Convergence
2606.rare_task_text: Find and regroup with your lost allies inside the anomaly.

2607.name: Chapter 5-6-2 - Deep Circulation
2607.rare_task_text: Make your way out of the zone.
